cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "datacentre_planning: UK data-centre planning-application dataset and triage pipeline"
abstract: >-
  Systematic national dataset of UK data-centre planning applications,
  with LLM-assisted triage to surface on-site power-generation signals
  buried in planning documents. Built in collaboration with the Guardian
  to support investigative journalism on data-centre carbon emissions.
